    "Clinical_Features": {
      "text": "Symptoms that have been associated with individuals with Blastocystis species in their stool include:\nWatery\ndiarrhea\n(may be acute or chronic)\nNausea\nAnorexia\nFatigue\nAbdominal cramping\nBloating\nFlatulence\nUrticaria\nGenerally patients are afebrile",
      "subsections": {},
      "tables": [],
